  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ravi Foundationproposes a project with an overall objective to prepare communities for disaster risk reduction and adopt effective mitigation strategies for safety of livestock and pet animals selected 40 rural communities for 5 union councils of district Tharparkar. These are areas which are affected by drought&amp; famine for the past many years. The primary focus is to Formation of Village Disaster Committees for the safety of Livestock and Pet Animals.</narrative>
